      <title><![CDATA[bat切换当前目录]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/06/20/bat/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line"> cd %~dp0</span><br><span class="line"> call git pull</span><br><span class="line"> xcopy D:\google\hosts\hosts C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\ /Y /R</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>每次更新host，使用管理员运行显示git失败，原因是使用管理员运行时，目录切换到system32下了。<br><code>cd %~dp0</code>表示切换回当前目录</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
